const getRandomNumber = (min, max) => Math.random() * (max - min) + min
getRandomNumber(2, 10)

const getRandomNumberInclusive = (min, max) => {
	min = Math.ceil(min)
	max = Math.floor(max)
	return Math.floor(Math.random() * (max - min + 1)) + min
}
getRandomNumberInclusive(2, 10)

export function quadratic(a, b, c) {
	if (nearlyEquals(a, 0) && nearlyEquals(b, 0)) return []
	if (nearlyEquals(a, 0)) return [-c / b]

	const p = -b / 2 / a
	const q = Math.sqrt(b * b - 4 * a * c) / 2 / a
	return [p + q, p - q]
}
